## Brand Consistency Workflow

- [ ] 1. Reference brand guidelines: Pull up brand book, logo usage rules, color palette, typography
- [ ] 2. Check visual elements: Logo placement, colors, fonts, imagery style
- [ ] 3. Check tone and voice: Does the copy sound like the brand?
- [ ] 4. Check messaging: Does the message align with current brand positioning?
- [ ] 5. Flag issues: Document any deviations from guidelines
- [ ] 6. Recommend fixes: Suggest specific corrections

## Key Inputs
- Brand: {{brand_name}}
- Creative asset: {{creative_asset}}
- Deliverable type: {{deliverable_type}}
- Channel: {{channel}}
